The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-25-2014 TUES

The Glenn Beck Program      
      
      Ferguson riots & history w/David Barton 11/25/14

Tuesday, November 25, 2014 


Glenn discusses the culpability of President Obama regarding 

    the troubles in Ferguson, 

     his encounter with a skunk and 
 
       America's reaction to Ferguson. 


    Plus, David Barton joins to talk about the history of 

       Thanksgiving and returning America to its roots. 


            That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
